\cf2 Topic Variations\
The same template works across multiple topics by changing what the chapters are about:\
Mental Health version: Each chapter addresses one anxiety/depression/overthinking pattern Mindset version: Each chapter reframes one limiting belief Productivity version: Each chapter installs one micro-habit or focus technique Communication version: Each chapter prepares the listener for one relational challenge that day Financial version: Each chapter shifts one money belief before the day's spending begins\
So for P5 Millennial Women alone, you could produce:\
